OL,3,CThe cancer side effects many men are
OL,4,Ctoo embarrassed to talk about
OL,6,FMarcus Grodentz, 73, from Magor in
OL,7,FSouth Wales was diagnosed with
OL,8,Fincurable prostate cancer in 2023.
OL,10,FMarcus said: "Before my treatment I
OL,11,Fhad difficulty controlling when I
OL,12,Fwould need the toilet. This led to the
OL,13,Foccasional embarrassing accident in
OL,14,Fpublic.
OL,16,F"Men especially are quite private and
OL,17,Fdon't want to share, and people can't
OL,18,Fhelp it but once they know about your
OL,19,Fcancer, they do treat you differently.
OL,20,FI miss that.
