OL,3,CThe cancer side effects many men are
OL,4,Ctoo embarrassed to talk about
OL,6,FFor Marcus he had experienced a range
OL,7,Fof symptoms following his diagnosis.
OL,9,F"Since having cancer, the side effects
OL,10,Fof the medication I'm on mean I have
OL,11,Fthe 'male menopause
OL,13,F"I am constantly tired; I get hot
OL,14,Fflushes; mood swings; I find myself
OL,15,Fsuddenly bursting into tears and I
OL,16,Fhave no control over it. My wife will
OL,17,Fask me what's wrong and I said, "I've
OL,18,Fgot no bloody clue.
