OL,3,CThe cancer side effects many men are
OL,4,Ctoo embarrassed to talk about
OL,6,F"There are some days when I feel
OL,7,Freally low and alone. I am still so
OL,8,Fconfused about everything.
OL,10,F"Me and my wife had a healthy sex life
OL,11,Feven in our 70's. We don't anymore. My
OL,12,Fwhole life has been turned upside
OL,13,Fdown, but this has been the biggest
OL,14,Fimpact. I feel guilty about that.
OL,16,F"It's like a huge part of my
OL,17,Frelationship has been removed. There's
OL,18,Fno desire.
