OL,3,CThe cancer side effects many men are
OL,4,Ctoo embarrassed to talk about
OL,6,F"Having prostate cancer means you need
OL,7,Fto go to the toilet all the time.
OL,8,FWhenever I would get near home, I
OL,9,Fwould need the loo, and you get to
OL,10,Fyour front door in an overwhelming
OL,11,Fpanic to turn the key and make it to
OL,12,Fthe toilet before you wet yourself."
OL,14,FMarcus found support in the men's
OL,15,Fgroup at Maggie's Cardiff, the cancer
OL,16,Fsupport centre based at The Velindre
OL,17,FHospital.
