OL,3,CThe cancer side effects many men are
OL,4,Ctoo embarrassed to talk about
OL,6,FHe said opening up about the more
OL,7,Fsensitive side effects of cancer
OL,8,Ftreatments have helped him feel less
OL,9,Falone.
OL,11,FMarcus said: "I told one of the other
OL,12,Fmen in the support group about
OL,13,Fconstantly thinking I might wet myself
OL,14,Fbefore I could open the front door to
OL,15,Fmy house and he said, "you know that's
OL,16,Fcalled front door syndrome. It's a
OL,17,Freal thing."
