OL,3,CThe cancer side effects many men are
OL,4,Ctoo embarrassed to talk about
OL,6,F"I never would have spoken to my
OL,7,Fconsultant or oncologist about that,
OL,8,Fbut it felt so validating that someone
OL,9,Felse had experienced this.
OL,11,F"When I started talking in the men's
OL,12,Fgroup about my disappearing penis, one
OL,13,Fof the other men stood up and shook my
OL,14,Fhand and said, "thank you Marcus, I
OL,15,Fthought it was just me."
OL,17,F"Us men are notoriously reluctant to
OL,18,Ftalk about intensely personal issues
OL,19,Fbut it's so important and that needs
OL,20,Fto change."
